<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Trondheim Premium Experience</title>

<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}

body{
    font-family:"Segoe UI",Arial;
    color:#333;
    line-height:1.6;
}

/* HERO */
header{
    background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.5), rgba(0,0,0,0.5)),
    url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500530855697-b586d89ba3ee') center/cover;
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    padding:120px 20px;
}

header h1{font-size:48px;margin-bottom:20px}
header p{font-size:20px;margin-bottom:25px}

/* BOTÕES */
.btn{
    background:#ff6b35;
    color:white;
    padding:14px 28px;
    text-decoration:none;
    border-radius:6px;
    display:inline-block;
    margin:5px;
    font-weight:bold;
}

.btn-secondary{
    border:2px solid white;
    background:transparent;
}

/* SEÇÕES */
.section{
    padding:70px 20px;
    text-align:center;
}

.section h2{
    font-size:32px;
    margin-bottom:20px;
}

/* CARDS */
.cards{
    display:flex;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
    gap:25px;
    justify-content:center;
    margin-top:30px;
}

.card{
    background:white;
    padding:25px;
    width:260px;
    border-radius:12px;
    box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

/* LISTA */
.list{
    max-width:600px;
    margin:auto;
    text-align:left;
    font-size:18px;
}

/* FORM */
form{
    max-width:450px;
    margin:auto;
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
}

input, textarea, select{
    margin:10px 0;
    padding:12px;
    border-radius:5px;
    border:1px solid #ccc;
}

button{
    background:#ff6b35;
    color:white;
    padding:14px;
    border:none;
    border-radius:5px;
    cursor:pointer;
}

/* WHATSAPP */
.whatsapp{
    position:fixed;
    bottom:20px;
    right:20px;
    background:#25d366;
    color:white;
    padding:15px 18px;
    border-radius:50%;
    text-decoration:none;
    font-size:22px;
}

/* FOOTER */
footer{
    background:#111;
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    padding:20px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>Trondheim Premium Experience</h1>
    <p>Uma semana de luxo, natureza e aventura na Noruega</p>

    #formularioQuero meu roteiro</a>
    #detalhesVer detalhes</a>
</header>

<section id="detalhes" class="section">
    <h2>Sua viagem exclusiva</h2>
    <p>Uma experiência pensada para brasileiros exigentes.</p>

    <div class="cards">
        <div class="card">
            <h3>🏨 Luxo</h3>
            <p>Hotéis 5 estrelas com vista para fiordes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>🍽️ Gourmet</h3>
            <p>Alta gastronomia com chefs locais.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>🚴 Aventura</h3>
            <p>Bike, caiaque e trilhas.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>🧭 Personalizado</h3>
            <p>Roteiro feito sob medida.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <h2>O que está incluído</h2>
    <div class="list">
        ✅ 7 dias em Trondheim <br>
        ✅ Hotel premium <br>
        ✅ Experiências gourmet <br>
        ✅ Passeios ativos <br>
        ✅ Guia em português <br>
        ✅ Suporte completo
    </div>
</section>

<section id="formulario" class="section">
